entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="昨日ゴミを漁ったら、吸入器がごっそり出てきたのよ" t="Fished through the dumpsters yesterday. Found a shit-ton o' huffers." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="よーく振れば、ひと吸い分くらいは残ってるっぽいの。ね、あんたも一緒にキメてみない？" t="There's gotta be at least one whiff left in each of 'em. Just gotta shake hard enough. C'mon, you wanna get skezzed?" b="" a=""/>
Gross, no way, dump that shit. We'll score ourselves some fresh dope.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="買うって、そんなお金持ってんの？" t="What? Since when do you have eddies?" b="" a=""/>
Started runnin' relaxation seminars at a veteran's center. Pay ain't bad for a corp gig.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="講師？ 資格とか持ってるの？" t="And you're, like, certified, or whatever?" b="" a=""/>
Pfff, no. I just tell them to imagine sand blowing in the wind and the sounds of rain on a river. Shit works.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="何それ。あたしもやりたい。まだインチキだってバレてないの？" t="Fuuuuck, I wouldn't mind a hustle like that. And nobody's found you out yet?" b="" a=""/>
The truth is, nobody really cares.
